The Telegraph - Calcutta : International
 Sunday, June 27, 2004 				 Bush in T-shirt
Newmarket-on-Fergus (Ireland), June 26 (Reuters): George W. Bush was caught on video wearing a T-shirt at the window of an Irish castle before meeting European leaders but summit organisers urged broadcasters not to use the image.																								A TV camera zoomed in on Bush looking out the window of his room at Dromoland Castle after his arrival yesterday evening. 																								The image of Bush was from the waist up. 																								Summit organisers appealed to news organisations covering the summit today not to use the video. 
